short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Google Chrome Extension to streamline access to Athabasca University Online Library Resources

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Allows students of Athabasca University to access online journals and periodicals using the Athabasca online Library.

This extension is not officially supported by or endorsed by Athabasca University.
